data.description: Welcome to this STUNNING custom-made home in the highly desirable North McAllen location of Orangewood Terrace. This modern and impeccable home boasts three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, and one office-study spread across one floor. As soon as you set foot into the house, you will be struck by the abundance of natural light, high ceilings, and modern living room  overlooking the beautiful backyard. The spacious master bedroom features a walk-in closet, double sink, and glass door shower, offering a feeling of luxury and comfort.    The heart of the home, the kitchen, is well-equipped with quartz countertops, decorative backsplash, and a eat-in bar  making it the perfect spot for cooking with your family.    Step outside into your PRIVATE OASIS, featuring a large backyard with a covered patio and a weather proof deck. The BEAUTIFUL swimming pool includes a waterfall, led lights ideal for hosting gatherings in the South Texas Summers.     Make an appointment today!
